# Drop-folder for the compiled RTMPE Roslyn analyzer DLLs
# (RTMPE.SDK.Analyzers.dll + its RTMPE.SDK.Conversion.Core.dll dependency).
#
# Populated at package time by scripts/package-analyzers.sh. The folder name
# carries a trailing '~' so the Unity asset pipeline ignores it (matching
# Samples~/ and Documentation~/), keeping the committed tree free of any
# unverified .meta. The final non-tilde, RoslynAnalyzer-labelled placement is
# resolved by the human-gated Unity load spike recorded in
# ../../Tooling/COMPILER_COMPATIBILITY.md.
